Prerequisites
-------------

- boost 1.41.0 or later
- optionally (WITH_SSL) openssl 0.9.8 or later

Compile and install boost
-------------------------

./bootstrap.sh --prefix=/tmpdir/boost-1_44_0
./bjam

configure SMERP in makefiles/gmake/config.mk and
set BOOST_DIR to /somewhere/boost-1_44_0 and set
BOOST_INCLUDE_DIRS and BOOST_LIB_DIR to the local
version

Compile and install openssl
---------------------------

Compile and install gtest
-------------------------

./configure
make
